== 2NT in competitive auctions

[#unified-leb]
=== Unified Lebensohl

Applies when: +
@ opps overcall our 1NT opening
_ with 2D, 2H or 2S +
@ we make a take-out double of their
_ weak-two (direct or balancing)

{reference}
https://bridgewinners.com/article/view/lebensohl-an-optimized-approach[
_Lebensohl, an Optimized Approach_]
__ {nbsp}{ndash}{nbsp} Gerben Dirkson +

==== Overview

@ 3{lab}unbid-suit{rab} = inv
@ neg. X then 3oM = Forcing (5*oM) +
@ cue-bid asks for stopper
@ 3NT shows a stopper +
@ direct cue-bid or 3NT (fast)
_ denies 4*oM +
@ 2NT then cue-bid or 3NT (slow)
_ shows 4*oM

